fj.data

Class IterableW<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fj.data.IterableW<A>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<A>

    public final class IterableW<A>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<A>
    A wrapper for Iterable that equips it with some useful functions.
